data.description: Villago must see! SO MANY UNIQUE FEATURES, This spacious home has 3 bedrooms plus an OFFICE, built in GARAGE CABINETS and SHOP. Located in a cul-de-sac. So many upgrades including flooring, kitchen cabinets, stainless steal appliances and ceiling fans. Butler's pantry, built in cabinets in bedroom, extra large laundry room, double sinks in both bathrooms, separate tub and shower in owner's suite. 2 dining areas. 2 living room areas. Covered patio, mature landscaping and garden boxes. Spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances and lots of counter space. SOLAR; Enjoy beautiful community amenities: ponds, parks, picnic areas, tennis, basketball, playgrounds & paved trails.
